      <h1>Forskrift om endring i forskrift om posisjonsgrenser for varederivater</h1>
      <section class="section" data-name="kapI" id="kapittel-1" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2019-01-16-26/KAPITTEL_1">
        <h2 data-text-align="center">I</h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1">I forskrift 20. desember 2017 nr. 2348 om posisjonsgrenser for varederivater gj&#xF8;res f&#xF8;lgende endringer:</article>
        <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">Ny hjemmel skal lyde:</article>
        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2">Fastsatt av Finanstilsynet 20. desember 2017 med hjemmel i lov 29. juni 2007 nr. 75 om verdipapirhandel (verdipapirhandelloven) &#xA7; 15-1 f&#xF8;rste ledd.</article>
        <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">&#xA7; 2 skal lyde:</article>
        <article class="futureLegalArticle" data-name="&#xA7;2" id="kapittel-1-foresl&#xE5;ttparagraf-1">
          <span class="futureLegalArticleHeader"><span class="legalArticleValue">&#xA7; 2</span>. <span class="legalArticleTitle">Posisjonsgrenser for likvide varederivater</span></span>
          <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-foresl&#xE5;ttparagraf-1-ledd-1">F&#xF8;lgende grenser for hvor store nettoposisjoner en fysisk eller juridisk person kan inneha i varederivater angitt i tabellen under, skal gjelde: <table><thead><tr><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Varederivat</i></th><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Handelsplass</i></th><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Venue Product Code</i></th><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Posisjonsgrense spotm&#xE5;neden</i></th><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Posisjonsgrense &#xF8;vrige m&#xE5;neder</i></th><th data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Enhet</i></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Farmed Salmon</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Fish Pool ASA</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">FPSA</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">23&#xA0;400 (24,9&#xA0;%)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">20&#xA0;800 (49,9&#xA0;%)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Lots</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Nordic Power (inc. Nordic EPADs)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Nasdaq Oslo ASA</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">ENO</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">19&#xA0;308&#xA0;181 (25&#xA0;%)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">67&#xA0;610&#xA0;330 (25&#xA0;%)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">MWh</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">German Power Base Load</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Nasdaq Oslo ASA</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">EDEBL</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">43&#xA0;362&#xA0;000 (25&#xA0;%)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">4&#xA0;277&#xA0;271 (50&#xA0;%)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">MWh</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">German Power Only Base Load</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">Nasdaq Oslo ASA</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">EDEFB Future</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">38&#xA0;903&#xA0;282 (25&#xA0;%)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">10&#xA0;618&#xA0;098 (50&#xA0;%)</td><td data-text-align="left" data-vertical-align="top">MWh</td></tr></tbody></table></article>
        </article>
      </section>
